{"tid":1471574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對噙日嘅事，信心產生動搖嘅人入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-14T09:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T09:22:30.000Z","uid":5327,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2fd2d37cfc0843f70464424c2051da5c7558f272","tid":1471574,"uid":5327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:59:45.000Z","msg":"記得連登有個comment, 你係呢個運動, 信奉嘅係一個信念，定係一個人、一個團隊？<br />\n<br />\n對我嚟講，揸緊個信念，知道要做啲咩同做到啲咩，就唔會再有咁易俾人帶風向，被啲鬼用啲卑劣手段分化。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n<br />\n唔係口講，係各位兄弟行歪左，都要包容不離不棄，暫緩送中，就係突破左和理非&amp;勇武嘅界線所得。<br />\n<br />\n我發夢就算上前最勁都係做救火隊同拆遷隊，明白前線好多好多變數，<br />\n<br />\n所以懇請和理非嘅各位，前線嘅各位兄弟姐妹，互相包容體諒+協助，一直以來我地跌跌撞撞咁行到宜家，連繫住大家，係一條睇唔見嘅線，唔好俾啲分化狗去整散我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我信前線會為件事好，做出當時可以做到嘅最好、最適合決定！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e59b93c730f33a6d54c6f6dcee674d601b76cfb","tid":1471574,"uid":5327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:07:30.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7bc475c29a35254d116e4df0cd70a68ead241ffd","tid":1471574,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:07:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66389592880ca74544df1485f14b22c132fe315f","tid":1471574,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=